---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /pending/
title: On the Desk
description: Pending slop sightings awaiting community votes.
robots: noindex, follow
---
<a class="back mono" href="{{ '/' | url }}">← all posts</a>

<h1 class="tagpage-title">On the <span class="tag">Desk</span></h1>

<p class="intro prose">
  Open submissions awaiting judgement. Hit 👍 on GitHub to push one over the
  bar — <strong>10 👍</strong> (with more 👍 than 👎) auto-publishes it.
</p>

{%- if pending.items and pending.items.length %}
<ol class="board">
  {%- for item in pending.items %}
  <li class="board-row">
    <a class="board-link" href="{{ item.url }}" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
      <span class="board-rank mono">{{ item.up }}👍</span>
      <span class="board-body">
        <span class="board-title">{{ item.title }}</span>
        <span class="board-stats mono">
          <span class="board-stat board-score">{{ item.up }} 👍</span>
          <span class="board-stat">{{ item.down }} 👎</span>
          <span class="board-stat">vote on GitHub →</span>
        </span>
      </span>
    </a>
  </li>
  {%- endfor %}
</ol>
{%- else %}
<p class="prose">
  Nothing on the desk right now.
  <a href="https://github.com/{{ site.repo }}/issues/new?template=slop-sighting.yml" rel="noopener">Submit a sighting →</a>
</p>
{%- endif %}
